---

## 4. Strategic Verdict & Risks

### The Verdict: APPROVE
Nvidia's current efficiency is so high (**$2.1M profit per employee**) that this expansion is statistically safe. The "Break-Even" revenue requirement is less than **2%** of our quarterly run-rate. 

### Risks to Watch
1.  **Talent Scarcity:** If the cost-per-head rises to $450k, our break-even requirement increases by 30%.
2.  **Execution Lag:** If sovereign contracts take 12+ months to sign (government bureaucracy), the "Margin Dip" will be deeper and longer than forecasted.

